				h1(style="font-size: 36px; line-height: 40px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -0.025em;") We’re changing the way people listen to ♬
				p(style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; color: #4B5563;") Sync-Audio’s team represents the finest music from emerging unsigned, Independent creators.
				p(style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; color: #4B5563;") Our platform was built on discovery where creative filmmakers can find fresh original songs/tracks for their project. We supply quality that’s accessible, affordable, without copyright issues.
				h1(style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -0.025em; padding-top: 20px;") Our Mission
				p(style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; color: #4B5563;") Sync-Audio was launched by music industry veteran Tesley Francis (alias T J Phillips). His own experience taught him the importance of protecting his content and maintaining an artistic independence.
				p(style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; color: #4B5563;") At Sync-Audio we are passionate about music and its crucial role in our lives. Our goal is to provide a fair revenue platform for independent artists and outstanding content to our clients.
				p(style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 32px; color: #4B5563;") Sync-Audio is also the only platform we know that promotes poetry recordings for licensing across various media industries.
